edit Dr. Maioriello for being able to go back to work 3 weeks after surgery with no restrictions.'),(47,32,'_edit_last','1'),(48,32,'_edit_lock','1421863360:1'),(49,32,'Procedure list','<ul>\r\n<li>Diagnostic Cerebral Angiogram</li>\r\n<li>Diagnostic Spinal Angiogram</li>\r\n<li>Coil Embolization of Cerebral Aneurysm</li>\r\n<li>Balloon Assisted Embolization of Cerebral Aneurysm</li>\r\n<li>Stent Assisted Embolization of Cerebral Aneurysm</li>\r\n<li>Cerebral Revascularization with Flow Diversion; Placement of Pipeline Embolization Device</li>\r\n<li>Intracranial Balloon Angioplasty for Vasospasm</li>\r\n<li>Infusion of Vasodilators for Vasospasm</li>\r\n<li>Embolization of Arteriovenous Malformation</li>\r\n<li>Embolization of Arteriovenous Malformation</li>\r\n<li>Embolization of Dural Arteriovenous Fistula</li>\r\n<li>Stent Placement for Intracranial Arterial Stenosis</li>\r\n<li>Stent Placement for Carotid Artery Stenosis</li>\r\n<li>Emergent Embolization of Life Threatening Epistaxis</li>\r\n<li>Emergent Embolization of Inaccessible Head and Neck Exsanguination</li>\r\n<li>Embolization of Extracranial Head and Neck tumors</li>\r\n<li>Embolization of Skull Base and Intracranial tumors</li>\r\n<li>Emergent Mechanical Thrombectomy for the treatment of Stroke</li>\r\n<li>Cerebral Angiography for Gamma Knife co-localization</li>\r\n<li>Balloon Test Occlusion</li>\r\n<li>Endovascular Intracranial Vessel Sacrifice</li>\r\n<li>Embolization of Carotid-Cavernous Fistula</li>\r\n<li>Intra-operative Cerebral Angiography</li>\r\n<li>Pediatric Diagnostic Cerebral Angiography</li>\r\n</ul>'),(52,34,'_edit_last','1'),(53,34,'_edit_lock','1421863155:1'),(54,34,'Procedure list','<ul>\r\n<li>Primary Brain Tumor Resection</li>\r\n<li>Metastatic Brain Tumor Resection</li>\r\n<li>Arteriovenous Malformation Resection</li>\r\n<li>Cerebral Aneurysm Clip Reconstruction</li>\r\n<li>Cavernous Angioma Resection</li>\r\n<li>Management of Closed Head Injury and Raised Intracranial Pressure</li>\r\n<li>Evacuation of Subdural and Epidural Hematoma</li>\r\n<li>Repair of Skull Base Fractures and Repair of CSF Leaks</li>\r\n<li>Evacuation of Intracerebral Hematoma from Hemorrhagic Stroke</li>\r\n<li>Decompressive Craniotomy for the Treatment of Malignant Intracranial Hypertension</li>\r\n<li>Cranioplasty</li>\r\n<li>Suboccipital Craniotomy for Chiari Malformation</li>\r\n<li>Endoscopic Transphenoidal Craniotomy for Pituitary Tumors and Sellar Lesions</li>\r\n<li>Ventriculo-Peritoneal Shunt Procedures for Normal Pressure Hydrocephalus and Obstructive Hydrocephalus</li>\r\n<li>Endoscopic Placement of Ventricular Catheter</li>\r\n<li>Endoscopic Cyst Fenestration</li>\r\n<li>Ommaya Reservoir Placement for Intrathecal Chemotherapy</li>\r\n</ul>'),(55,35,'_edit_last','1'),(56,35,'_edit_lock','1429298732:1'),(57,35,'Procedure list','<ul>\r\n<li>Cerivcal Arthoplasty</li>\r\n<li>Anterior Cervical Discectomy and Corpectomy</li>\r\n<li>Anterior/Posterior 360º Cervical Fusion for Deformity Correction and Cervical Spondylotic Myelopathy</li>\r\n<li>Cervical, Thoracic, Lumbar Trauma Surgery</li>\r\n<li>Revision of Cervical, Thoracic, Lumbar Spine Surgery</li>\r\n<li>Removal of Spinal Column and Spinal Cord Tumors</li>\r\n<li>Thoracotomy/Retroperitoneal Approach for Thoracic Vertebrectomy</li>\r\n<li>Minimally Invasive Microdiscectomy and Lumbar Laminectomy</li>\r\n<li>Minamally Invasive Lumbar Fusions</li>\r\n<li>Minimally Invasive Spinal Deformity Correction</li>\r\n<li>Nucleoplasty (percutaneous disc decompression)</li>\r\n<li>Shunting of Spinal Cord Syringomyelia (Syrinx)</li>\r\n<li>Treatment of failed Black Syndrome</li>\r\n<li>Implantation and Revision of Baclofen and Morphine Pumps</li>\r\n<li>Kyphoplasty and Vertebroplasty (percutaneous treatment of compression fractures)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(62,36,'_edit_last','1'),(63,36,'_edit_lock','1426026529:1'),(64,36,'_wp_page_template','default'),(65,47,'_wp_attached_file','2015/01/Consult_Request_MIBS.pdf'),(66,20,'_wp_page_template','default'),(70,56,'_edit_last','1'),(71,56,'_edit_lock','1429641291:1'),(73,56,'quote','On June 4, 2007, our lives changed forever. That day, our Mom, grandma, great-grandma, sister, aunt, wife, and friend to all, Pam A., suffered a major stroke. By no coincidence, God sent Dr. Maioriello to help.'),(74,57,'_edit_last','1'),(75,57,'_edit_lock','1429304745:1'),(76,57,'quote','Dr. Maioriello is very skilled and honest and gives you the information needed to make the decision, if surgery is your answer.'),(78,58,'_edit_last','1'),(79,58,'_edit_lock','1429641097:1'),(80,58,'quote','Thank you Dr. Maioriello for everything you and your team did for Scott. Your family has been great too. Sophia and Gia will always have a special place in our hearts as well as Bell and your self.'),(82,59,'_edit_last','1'),(83,59,'_edit_lock','1429304714:1'),(85,59,'quote','I would recommend Doctor Anthony V. Maioriello to anyone in the world for this operation if needed.'),(86,60,'_edit_last','1'),(87,60,'_edit_lock','1429304145:1'),(88,60,'quote','I am now 99% recovered from my spinal problems and I credit Dr. Maiorello for my major improvement.'),(90,61,'_edit_last','1'),(91,61,'_edit_lock','1429303986:1'),(94,62,'_edit_last','1'),(95,62,'_edit_lock','1429303951:1'),(96,62,'quote','You and Bella have helped us so much that we wanted to show some gratitude and to say, “Thank You.”'),(98,63,'_edit_last','1'),(99,63,'_edit_lock','1429303939:1'),(100,63,'quote','This is a once in a lifetime event and I am forever grateful.'),(102,64,'_edit_last','1'),(103,64,'_edit_lock','1429640990:1'),(104,64,'quote','I was taken off the breathing machine in less then 24 hours of the surgery and was released home after one week.'),(106,65,'_edit_last','1'),(107,65,'_edit_lock','1429641060:1'),(108,65,'quote','He saved my life, and I would highly recommend him to everyone I know.'),(110,66,'_edit_last','1'),(111,66,'_edit_lock','1429303596:1'),(112,66,'quote','I am thankful for you, your skill an