res to treat these diseases affecting the brain, blood vessels, and their supporting structures.','Brain','','publish','closed','closed','','brain','','','2015-01-21 17:59:15','2015-01-21 17:59:15','',0,'/?post_type=procedures&#038;p=34',0,'procedures','',0),(35,1,'2013-01-21 15:27:34','2013-01-21 15:27:34','Utilizing minimally invasive muscle sparing tubular retractors when performing spine surgery has been basis of our core belief. Surgery should be performed with as little harm to the patient as possible. From simple laminectomies to complicated intradural intramedullary spinal cord tumors and reconstructive fusion operations; patients can have less post-operative pain and a quicker less debilitating recovery.','Spine','','publish','closed','closed','','spine','','','2015-04-17 19:27:15','2015-04-17 19:27:15','',0,'/?post_type=procedures&#038;p=35',0,'procedures','',0),(36,1,'2015-01-21 21:19:48','2015-01-21 21:19:48','<div class=\"addresses\"><a href=\"javascript: void(0)\" id=\"htxLocation\"><strong>Houston Office</strong><br />\r\n3400 Bissonnet St.<br /> Suite 220<br />\r\nHouston, TX 77005</a><a href=\"javascript: void(0)\" id=\"clLocation\"><strong>Clear Lake Office</strong><br />\r\n450 W Medical Center Blvd<br /> Suite 510<br />\r\nWebster, TX 77598</a></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"callApp\">Call our office to schedule an appointment:</h3>\r\n<p><strong>HOURS: M-F 9AM–5PM</strong><br />\r\nToll-Free (800) 323-6427 | Local (281) 652-5500 | Fax (713) 664-4488</p>','Locations','','publish','closed','open','','locations','','','2015-03-10 22:27:12','2015-03-10 22:27:12','',0,'/?page_id=36',0,'page','',0),(37,1,'2015-01-21 21:19:48','2015-01-21 21:19:48','Houston Office\r\n3400 Bissonnet St Suite 220\r\nHouston, TX 77005\r\n\r\nClear Lake Office\r\n450 W Medical Center Blvd Suite 510\r\nWebster, TX 77598\r\n\r\nCall our office to schedule an appointment:\r\n\r\nHOURS: M-F 9AM–5PM\r\nTollFree (800) 323-6427 | Local (281) 652-5500 | Fax (7130 664-4488','Locations','','inhe